# Frontend Conventions

## Architecture

- React 19 SPA with React Router v6 (routes: `/` landing, `/app` dashboard).
- State: local `useState` in App.jsx. No Redux/Zustand. Auth token in `localStorage`.
- Styling: styled-components (in `src/styled/`) + Tailwind CSS. Theme in `src/styled/theme.js`.
- HTTP: axios with `API_BASE` from `src/apiBase.js`.

## Components

- `src/App.jsx`: Main app with auth, dashboard, admin panel (large file, ~2000 lines).
- `src/components/`: Extracted components (FilterConfiguration, GeneratedFiles, LandingPage, ProcessingHistory).
- `src/styled/`: Styled component definitions organized by feature area.

## API Calls

- All API calls use axios with `API_BASE` prefix.
- Auth header: `Authorization: Bearer ${token}` (token from localStorage).
- Error extraction: use `getApiErrorMessage()` from `src/utils/getApiErrorMessage.js`.

## Testing

- Unit: Vitest + React Testing Library. Config in `tests/vitest.config.js`. Tests in `tests/unit/`.
- E2E: Playwright (Chromium). Config in `playwright.config.js`. Tests in `tests/e2e/`.
- API coverage: `tests/unit/api/api-coverage.test.js` verifies all backend endpoints are tested.
- Setup file: `tests/vitest.setup.js` (localStorage mock, location mock, matchMedia mock, fetch mock).

## File Structure

```
src/
  App.jsx          # Main app (auth + dashboard + admin)
  apiBase.js       # API URL config
  main.jsx         # Entry point (excluded from coverage)
  components/      # Extracted React components
  styled/          # Styled-components by feature
  utils/           # Utility functions
```
